                    <span>I originally obtained this book from the local library and immediately realized that I wanted to own it as a reference.  Very good, detailed material about running a retail business.  Highly recommended.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Good Starting Point</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
